        contains a lot of bug, be unstable, kills panda etc.

        Please repport any bugs/suggestions to "team @t tatoeba dOt org" 
    </div>
    <div class="module">
        <h2>Random Sentence</h2>
        
        <p>
            Show another
            <a href="<% url "/sentences/show-random" %>" >
